race.description: Gundagai District Services Hair Of The Dog Hcp
race.comment: SOUTHERN DANCER (6) peaks and seeks the hat-trick off a narrow defeat at Randwick over a mile. Just missed prior in this grade at Wagga Riverside, and the top hoop is reunited from that. Can settle forward and is well-placed. MAID IN DUBAI (2) just missed behind the above at Wagga Riverside, and then tackled Open grade at Berrigan and was nudged out as a short-priced favourite. She should enjoy the run of the race and has decent claims. BURGUNDY GIRL (5) comes back in distance following a 2.7L defeat at Warwick Farm in much stronger. Maps well, and the 3kg claim brings her into it. AMBER STAR (7) couldn't reel in the winner at Albury last start after a strong effort at Wangaratta the start prior. Shapes nicely for this off those efforts however and he's right in the mix.
